on dom0 
--------------

- create tmpfs 
    mkdir /image_tmpfs
    sudo mount -t tmpfs -o size=3G,mode=700 tmpfs /image_tmpfs

-updated current directory to LD_LIBRARY_PATH
    export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=`pwd`:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH

- update XEN_BR0_IP in xapi_config.py and start proxy server 
    chmod a+x xapi_proxy.py
    nohup python xapi_proxy.py & 

restart nova compute after this change


building rpclient.py bindings
--------------
If you want to build rpclient python bindings then do the following

cd RPCore/src/rptest/vmstart/
make -f rpclient-g.mak
copy rpclient.py, _rpclient.so and librputil.so to current directory





